                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970426-82-defend658 t17970426-82-punish460"></join>
               Publickly whipped
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. Justice BULLER.</p>
